TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Theory of Inventory Decisions
AU  - Mills, Edwin S.
AB  - [This article is an attempt to determine whether firms can be assumed to behave as if they were using a rational inventory policy. A decision rule is deduced from a plausible model of a firm's cost structure and an attempt is made to see whether historical time series of firms' production, sales, and inventory data can be explained by such a decision rule.]
C1  - Full publication date: Apr., 1957
DB  - JSTOR
